# üçΩÔ∏è Zomato Dataset Visualization Project

## üéØ Objective
To extract, analyze, and visualize insights from the Zomato dataset using appropriate and interactive charts. This project helps users explore cuisine preferences, pricing patterns, and restaurant distributions across Indian cities.

---

## ‚úÖ Create Meaningful Visualizations

### üìä Selection of Chart Types

| Chart Type        | Purpose                                                 | Example                                   |
|-------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| **Bar/Column**     | Compare categories                                       | Top-rated cuisines by city                |
| **Pie/Donut**      | Show proportions                                          | Cuisine distribution                      |
| **Scatter Plot**   | Show correlations                                        | Rating vs Cost                             |
| **Line Chart**     | Display trends over time                                | Monthly orders (hypothetical/extended)    |
| **Heatmap**        | Highlight intensity in two variables                    | Average rating by city                    |
| **Map**            | Show geographic distribution                            | Restaurant density across India           |

